dct_title_s: A new map of the United States : upon which are delineated its vast works of internal communication, routes across the continent &c., showing also Canada and the island of Cuba
dct_description_sm: Compiled, drawn & engraved by W. Williams, practical geographer and engraver, Philadelphia.; Insets: Map of California, Oregon, New Mexico, Utah &c. -- Map of the island of Cuba -- City & harbor of Havana -- Map of the Niagara River and Falls.; Prime meridians: Greenwich and Washington, D.C.; Removed from: Baldwin, Thomas. A new and complete gazetteer of the United States. Philadelphia: Lippincott, Grambo & co., 1854.
